_sText: Hello Peoples :) So i played the all-time-classic fy_Buzzkill and had the idea to turn it into a gungame map with a different theme and more detailed. If you need any information about the map, permission to edit or anything else just contact me on steam: audiOtrash is the SteamID name ;) Please contact me too for critics and stuff that you want/need added :) I hope you'll enjoy this map and if you decide to upload it to your server leave a comment with the ip :)
